title: Suicide Squad Is Terrible And Should Fail...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the newest live-service slop of this year known as "Suicide Squad: Kill The Justice League." Why Rocksteady and WB decided to release this game with an online only requirement when they're own servers can't handle a smaller player load is beyond me. Thanks for watching!
